author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Euronext Announces Listing of Digital Biotech Voluntis
text:
May 30 (Reuters) - EURONEXT:
* ADMISSION AND ISSUE PRICE WAS SET AT EUR 14 PER SHARE * MARKET CAPITALISATION WAS EUR 105.9 MILLION ON THE DAY OF LISTING
* OFFERING RAISED EUR 30.1 MILLION ALTOGETHER Source : bit.ly/2JeYj0u
